I
NTRODUCTION
​
This Privacy Policy applies to watch faces, apps, websites and related services, which I refer to here as “Services”. I reserve the right to change this policy from time to time, so be sure to check it periodically. Your continued use of the Services after the effective date will be governed by the new Privacy Policy.
By downloading, accessing watch faces and applications that I have released, or interacting with my websites or other Services, you unconditionally agree to the terms of their use.
​
COLLECTION AND STORAGE OF USER DATA
​
As such, I am not in the business of collecting and transmitting user information to any services, including advertising agents and counter-agents. The data that you leave to interact with my services is used only for your identification when communicating with me and gaining access to certain pages of sites and content.
You can delete your registration on my websites at any time, losing access to certain content, with the possibility of restoring access by re-registering.
